sequenceDiagram
  participant User as User
  participant NotionAgent as Notion Agent
  participant Worker as Notion Worker
  participant Notion as Notion API
  participant Libretto as Libretto Cloud

  User->>NotionAgent: workflow build request (intent + initial_url, optional credential_id)

  NotionAgent->>Notion: create database with schema matching request
  Notion-->>NotionAgent: database_id + databaseUrl

  NotionAgent->>Worker: call buildWorkflow(databaseUrl, initial_url, prompt, credential_id?)

  Worker->>Notion: retrieve database schema
  Notion-->>Worker: database properties

  Worker->>Worker: append JSON output instructions to prompt

  Worker->>Libretto: POST /v1/workflows/build
  Note over Worker,Libretto: Sends prompt, initial_url,<br/>params.database_id,<br/>and credential_id if provided

  Libretto-->>Worker: build_id
  Worker-->>NotionAgent: return build_id
  NotionAgent-->>User: build started (build_id)

  loop Until build is ready
    NotionAgent->>Worker: call checkBuild(build_id)
    Worker->>Libretto: POST /v1/workflows/buildStatus
    Libretto-->>Worker: status, attempted_steps, workflow_name
    Worker-->>NotionAgent: build status
  end

  NotionAgent-->>User: workflow ready (workflow_name)
